content: Hello - I completed the training recently and I don't think I have been added to the Text Team. I'd love to be added. Let me know if I missed a step in the process. Thanks!

Hi <@788484968002093097> we appreciate you are excited to get started. Text team is onboarding folks. Please check in https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1266829704204386334 and look for a DM (it will show as a red dot on the game player icon in the top left of your screen).
